 «- -----------------------------------------------------------\\/--------- -»

@{i}       The Installation@{ui}
@{fg fill}   ·- ------------------ -·@{fg text}

Copy all files to their drawers in "Fame:".

The included executable "FileReverse.fim" has been optimized for the 68020
processor. Patches for 68000/68030/68040/68060 processors can be found in
drawer "Patches/". (Why waste kilobytes of download space if the several
executabls differ only by hundreds of bytes ?)

 «- ---------------------------------------------------------------------- -»

