@node Ton! " What happened to ton! ?"

  Well, We decided to change the name from Type o'Negative to Desaster.
  Nothing else.

  Usally Desaster was a commodore 64 group (but still inactive) and both
  (Tolpan and me) were members of Dtr, and so we decide to change the
  group name cause i think Desaster is much better name for a group as Ton!
  Nothing else has been changed with the group members.

  /Mogue

  Desaster exist of
  -----------------
     ( Mogue! - Coder and sysop )    Tolpan - Coder and sysop
  Gravedancer - Coder and sysop        Newt - Coder and sysop
                                                               .... Wow!

  This was just to inform you before you start thinking someone of the
  old Ton! crew has left to build up a new group called Desaster!.

@endnode
